# React (example — enable at bootstrap)

Copy to `.cursor/rules/react.mdc` (or your stack name) and set `alwaysApply: true`.

- **Components:** presentational vs container boundaries — no API calls in leaf UI components unless project convention says otherwise
- **State:** local state for UI-only; shared state via project store pattern (document in ADR or overview)
- **Hooks:** custom hooks for reusable logic; one concern per hook
- **Data fetching:** centralized client layer — not scattered `fetch` in pages
- **Tests:** component/integration tests for user-visible behavior; avoid snapshot-only tests
- **Accessibility:** semantic HTML and labels for forms — per product brief
